=head1 DESCRIPTION

The retry strategy that's associated with a job. For more information,
see Automated job retries
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/batch/latest/userguide/job_retries.html)
in the I<Batch User Guide>.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 Attempts => Int

The number of times to move a job to the C<RUNNABLE> status. If the
value of C<attempts> is greater than one, the job is retried on failure
the same number of attempts as the value.



